WEBVTT

00:00:03.280 --> 00:00:09.160
Arianna Huffington: So, April 2007
I actually collapsed.

00:00:09.800 --> 00:00:11.896
Adam Grant: That's Arianna Huffington.

00:00:11.920 --> 00:00:15.176
Two years earlier,
she had started "The Huffington Post."

00:00:15.200 --> 00:00:17.256
Now she was lying
on the floor of her office

00:00:17.280 --> 00:00:18.816
in her New York apartment

00:00:18.840 --> 00:00:20.936
in a pool of her own blood.

00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:23.456
AH: I had just gotten the news

00:00:23.480 --> 00:00:28.576
that I had been picked as one
of "Time's" 100 most influential people

00:00:28.600 --> 00:00:33.576
and as I came to in my pool of blood
having broken my cheekbone,